title: Kupp totals 4 TDs as Eastern Washington tops Idaho St 45-28
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Cooper Kupp caught two touchdowns, threw for one and returned a punt for a score as Eastern Washington handled Idaho State 45-28 on Saturday...
